description: Aspose.PDF for C++ is a native C++ library that enables the developers to add PDF handling capabilities to their C++ applications. The library allows to perform a wide range of document processing tasks including creation of PDF files, form processing, text and page manipulation, management of annotations, attachments, bookmarks, custom font handling and much more.
summary: Aspose.PDF for C++ is a native C++ library that enables the developers to add PDF handling capabilities to their C++ applications.
title: Aspose.PDF for C++
